    skos:notation "2013" ;
    skos:prefLabel "Council of Ministers head will also include the salary and allowances of ‘Parliamentary Secretaries’. The expenditure on personal staff attached to Ministers/Deputy Ministers etc. will be recorded under Secretariat expenditure major head concerned except in the case of Prime Minister's office, which will be recorded under the minor head ‘Prime Minister's office’ under this major head. charges, maintenance and running of vehicles etc; rent of buildings, if any, acquired for residence of Ministers, and paid by the Public Works Department will, however, be recorded under ‘2216-Housing 01-Government. Residential Buildings-Lease charges’."@en .

