on General or other Reserve Funds’ below sub-major head ’05-Interest on Reserve Funds’ under ‘MH 2049-Interest Payments’. Governments’ and Minor Heads ‘101’ to ‘105’ under Sub-Major Head ‘02-Interest from Union Territory Governments with Legislatures’ will continue to operate till earlier loans are fully repaid. separate sub heads may be opened under this Minor Head for each type of Interest- Bearing Advances."@en .

