    skos:prefLabel "General bungalows, hotels etc. under concerned minor heads. tourist centres excluding that allocable to other minor heads e.g. expenditure on a bus shelter or booking office will be recorded under ‘Tourist Transport Service’. allocable to other minor heads and also publicity either direct or through other bodies. well as operational expenditure of Tourist Transport services including subsidies to agencies operating Air, Road and Water Transport services for Tourists. Foreign Trade and Export 3453 Promotion development but excludes items relating to the minor head ‘Export subsidy’. Census Surveys and 3454 Statistics"@en .

