    skos:prefLabel "General major head by the P&T Board depending upon the necessity: - (i) Land (ii) Building (iii) Apparatus and Plant (iv) Teleprinter and subscriber's installations (v) Motor vehicles and launches (vi) Installation Test equipment (vii) Cables (viii) Lines and Wires (ix) Subscribers' Installations (x) Direction and Administration (xi) Masts and Aerials (xii) Direction and Execution Consultants India Ltd.’ Postal and Telecom wings, it forms part of Telecommunications wing. Accordingly the capital expenditure on this wing forms part of the capital outlay on Telecommunications. not be operational for fresh transactions w.e.f. 01-04-2019. Capital Outlay on Satellite 5252 system transactions w.e.f. 2016-17."@en .

